--- 4th December 2013 --- This version of the UML model represents a SIG 3D consolidated UML model in the variant which represents the geometry objects as associations. Contributions to this version have been by SIG 3D and CityGML SWG as well as Jürgen Ebbinghaus, Tatjana Kutzner, Andreas Donaubauer and Thomas H. Kolbe.
--- 20th September 2013 --- This UML model has been remodeled based on the CityGML specification 2.0 by AED-SICAD AG (Jürgen Ebbinghaus) by order of AGeoBW Amt für Geoinformationswesen der Bundeswehr.
Afterwards, the model has been checked and edited by Technische Universität München, Chair of Geoinformatics (Tatjana Kutzner, Andreas Donaubauer, Thomas H. Kolbe).
In September 2013 the model was donated to the public by AGeoBW and AED-SICAD AG in order to support further CityGML development.
